selene (16.2.1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * App settings: Allow user to enter backup path and output path

  * App settings: Updated checkboxes for selecting directories
  
  * App settings: Added option to choose between 'ffmpeg' and 'avconv'

  * App settings: Added option to select media player
  
  * Added thumbnail image for audio files

  * Added option to encode audio with FFmpeg's Native AAC encoder

  * Added support for encoding with Fraunhofer FDK AAC encoder (aac-enc)

  * Added option to change AAC profile

  * Removed the 'Preview Output' right-click option in file list
  
  * Folders can be dragged and dropped on the main window to add files

  * Updated toolbar items for adding and removing files

  * Show icon beside file name in list view

  * Various minor changes

 -- Tony George <tony.george.kol@gmail.com>  Wed, 10 Feb 2016 10:00:00 +0530
